  "text": "For comparison, proteins from young tomato leaves (taken from the top most branch of the plant) were analyzed following the same plant treatments (L-C, L-E-C, L-HS, L-E-HS samples, respectively). Three biological replicates of each treatment (from both pollen and leaves) were analyzed and separated into two fractions via SDS-PAGE prior to tryptic digestion and LC-MS/MS analysis similar to [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Supplementary Tables S1, S2 include all identified pollen and leaf proteins, respectively.",
